# Jo Ann Walczak — Writer Website

Personal one-page static site for author Jo Ann Walczak. Audience: readers; goal: introduce the author and link to books, blog, and social.

## Stack

- **Astro 4** — static site generator; no SSR, no React/Vue.
- **Tailwind CSS** — styling only; use theme tokens from `tailwind.config.mjs` (ink, surface, paper, muted, accent, font-display, font-body, max-w-prose, max-w-content).
- **Minimal JS** — only where needed (e.g. smooth scroll); prefer HTML/CSS.

## Structure

- `src/pages/index.astro` — single page; composes layout + section components.
- `src/layouts/Layout.astro` — shell, meta, fonts.
- `src/components/` — Header, Hero, About, Books, Blog, Connect, Footer. One concern per component.
- `public/` — static assets (favicon, images); reference by path e.g. `/image.jpg`.

## Conventions

- Keep the site static and fast; no backend or CMS.
- Preserve the dark, elegant theme: ink background, paper text, surface for sections, accent (gold) for links/CTAs.
- When adding content (bio, books, blog URL, social links), edit the relevant component; add short comments for placeholders.
- Use semantic HTML and accessible patterns (e.g. `aria-label` on nav, alt on images).
